column2: SELECT   s.specobjID, s.bestobjID, s.firstrelease, s.survey, s.sourcetype, s.class,   gal.ra, gal.raErr, gal.dec, gal.decErr, s.z, s.zErr, s.zwarning,    gal.r, gal.i, gal.g, gal.dered_r, gal.dered_i, gal.dered_g, gal.psfMag_r, gal.modelMag_r, gal.petroMag_r, gal.extinction_r, gal.petroR5#_r    gal.psfMag_g, gal.modelMag_g, gal.extinction_g into mydb.LRG_FROM_galaxy_with_spec from SpecObj as s   join Galaxy as gal on gal.ObjID = s.bestobjID where   ( flags & (dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) + dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) + dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)) ) > #    and ( flags & (dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) + dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) + dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)) ) != dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)    and ( flags & (dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&) + dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)) ) = #
